@startuml FR-12_Usage_Logging

title Activity Diagram: FR-12 - Usage Logging

|System|
start

:Reservation Event Occurs;

if (Event Type?) then (Creation)
  :Capture Reservation Creation Data;
  note right
    - User
    - Asset
    - Start Time
    - End Time
    - Status: "Created"
  end note
  
  :Record Usage Log Entry;
  
  :Store Log with Creation Status;
  
else (Completion)
  :Capture Reservation Completion Data;
  note right
    - User
    - Asset
    - Start Time
    - End Time
    - Status: "Completed"
  end note
  
  :Record Usage Log Entry;
  
  :Store Log with Completion Status;
  
endif

:Usage Log Recorded Successfully;

stop


@enduml
